  * NumPy 		1.9.1
  * SciPy 		0.15.0
  * weave 		0.15.0
  * Matplotlib 	1.4.2
  * mpmath 		0.18
  * numexpr 	2.2.2
  * netCDF4 	1.1.3
  * pp 		1.6.4
  * mpi4py		1.3.1
  * futures		2.2.0
  * PypeR 		1.1.2
  * inspyred            1.0

### ------------------- R ###
  * R		3.1.2
  * R-Packages: raster


### ------------------ Library ###
  * Blas && Lapack	3.5.0
  * HDF5		1.8.12
  * netCDF		4.3.2
  * netCDF-fortran	4.4.1
  * nco		4.4.4
  * gsl		1.16
